context.text: Mongkol Borei District - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
, which are further subdivided into 157 villages ( phum ).
The district is subdivided into 13 communes ( khum )
The main roads passing through the district are National Highway 5 and 6 .
The Mongkol Borei River forms the district boundary to the east towards Preah Netr Preah.
Neighboring districts are (from the northwest clockwise) Malaii , Ou Chrov , Serei Saophoan and Preah Netr Preah of Banteay Meanchey, Thma Koul , Bavel and Sampov Loun of Battambang Province
Stung Mongkol Borei Sub-Basin . Asian Development Bank.
